metadata.name: Salisby Dalisby new Metaverse Home
metadata.description: After fourty years of very long hours and extra effort in planning the last metaverse home is completed in the family complex of twenty three new homes. Salisby Dalisby abandons his beautiful lighted plate home and takes his family to the new much larger custom home.  Salisby follows his sons, his dear wife holding their new born daughter into the entrance of the metaverse home. The dark lords have a very unpleasant surprise as the family moves deeper into the home entrance.
